{
  "texts": [
    "To further verify the ef- fectiveness of the proposed MagicTime Recipe (e.g., Magic Adaptive Strategy, Dynamic Frame Extraction, and Magic Text Encoder), we then integrate it into the DiT-based framework [3], [79], [80].",
    "We select Open-Sora-Plan v1.0.0 [80] as a representative, given its superior performance in generating landscape videos.",
    "We then expand the dataset with additional metamorphic landscape time-lapse videos using the same annotation framework to create the ChronoMagic-Landscape dataset.",
    "Subsequently, we train Open-Sora-Plan v1.0.0 with this dataset and our MagicTime Recipe.",
    "As illustrated in Fig. 12, our model can generate high-quality metamorphic landscape time-lapse videos, whereas the baseline model produces nearly static videos."
  ]
}